<author>mfdy mwsy̱, lydyạ sẖdyd</author>
<title>klmn rby qlby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- klmn rby qlby bạlṣmt wạlskwn
 ạ̉hms fy ạ̉dẖny wʿdk &quot;wḥdk ln tkwn&quot;
 ḥbb lnfsy qwlk fy ạlạmn wạlsẖjwn
 yḥlw lnfsy ḥmdk yạrby ạlḥnwn

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: rby ạ̉hms fy ạ̉dẖny bwʿdk ạltẖmyn
   tḥẓy̱ bạlnṣr yạ ạ̉bny fy sẖkẖṣy ạlạmyn
   klmny kl ywm bạlḥq wạlyqyn
   ạ̉smʿny hms ḥbk &quot;lst blạ mʿyn&quot;

[V2]
 2- klm rby ʿbydk qdhm fy ṭrqk
 kẖyrạaⁿ ạ̉fḍ ʿlyhm zdhm mn ḥqk
 yṣbḥwạ ṭwʿ ạ̉mrk ḥbạaⁿ lsẖkẖṣk
 ḥty̱ tjỷ sryʿạaⁿ yḥẓwạ bmdḥk

[V3]
 3- rby ạ̉ksẖf ly ʿn fkrk ksạlf ạlạ̉yạm
 ạ̉ftḥ qlby fạ̉ʿrf ḥqk bạltmạm
 ky ạ̉lhj bḥmdk ṭwʿạaⁿ ʿly̱ ạldwạm</lyrics>
</song>